grondag.frex.api.model

Interface DynamicBakedModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    net.fabricmc.fabric.api.renderer.v1.model.FabricBakedModel

    @API(status=STABLE)
public interface DynamicBakedModel
extends net.fabricmc.fabric.api.renderer.v1.model.FabricBakedModel
    Interface for baked models that output meshes with enhanced rendering features. Can also be used to generate or customize outputs based on world state instead of or in addition to block state when render chunks are rebuilt.

    Note for Renderer implementors: Fabric causes BakedModel to extend this interface with FabricBakedModel.isVanillaAdapter() == true and to produce standard vertex data. This means any BakedModel instance can be safely cast to this interface without an instanceof check.
